Best ah vibe dia. Tak pack and crowded like jb area. Also, because of the view is the immigration building untuk masuk singapore kan, boleh lah duduk duduk, layan char kuey teow sambil ambik mood nak kerja singapore. Lah! Tibe.

Also, there‚Äôs a surau nearby, So kalau you came around prayer time, dapat lah layan char kuey teow sambil dengan reciting from imam üëç

Google 'Charkweyteow Gelang Patah' for exact location. Food was good, got one special n one kerang char kuey tiao only Rm19. Free flow water, and cili. Business runs by 3 young male, 2 cooks and 1 taking orders. They'll announce your name when your order is complete, so pls pay attention. Not enough table, chairs and light to cover the whole area, but parking was easy since it is by the road. Come only when the weather is great, since there's no shade. You can bring your own table/chair.
Have to wait almost 2 hours for the food! Gas habis lah, pes habis lah. Service tolong improve.
Not suitable for babies and toddler because there‚Äôs smoker
